<item>
            <title>[HIVE-26597] Fix unsetting of db prop repl.target.for in ReplicationSemanticAnalyzer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-26597</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when repl policy is set from A -&amp;gt; B&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;repl.target.for&lt;/b&gt;&#160;is set on B.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;when failover is initiated&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;repl.failover.endpoint&lt;/b&gt;&#160;=&#160;&lt;b&gt;&apos;TARGET&apos;&lt;/b&gt;&#160;is set on B.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;now when reverse policy is set up from&#160;&lt;b&gt;A &amp;lt;- B&lt;/b&gt;;&lt;br/&gt;
there is a check in&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/master/ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/parse/ReplicationSemanticAnalyzer.java#L196&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;ReplicationSemanticAnalyzer#initReplDump&lt;/a&gt;&#160;which checks for existence of these two properties and if they are set,&lt;br/&gt;
it unsets the&#160;&lt;b&gt;repl.target.for&lt;/b&gt;&#160;property.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Because of this optimisedBootstrap won&apos;t be triggered because it checks for the existence of&#160;&lt;b&gt;repl.target.for&lt;/b&gt;&#160;property during repl dump on target&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/master/ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/exec/repl/OptimisedBootstrapUtils.java#L93&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;HERE&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fix : remove the code which unsets repl.target.for in ReplicationSemanticAnalyzer, because second dump cycle of optimized bootstrap unsets it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
